history.content:
Hi, I'm trying to waitlist for 161 with the 999 discussion section. However, when I try to add the class directly, the 999 section doesn't show up when I'm asked to select a discussion section. On the other hand, when I try to add the class by adding it to my shopping cart first, I can see the 999 section just fine in Schedule Planner, but when I send it to my shopping cart, only the lecture gets saved; then when I try to enroll, it gives me an error saying I need to select a discussion section. Am I understanding the purpose and usage of 999 sections properly? Does this have anything to do with 161 having reached 70% capacity?

Thanks.
history.subject: Enrolling in 999 sections
